title: Russians Named in Trump Dossier Dismiss Claims
text:
Russians Named in Trump Dossier Dismiss Claims They were incredulous over allegations of ties to Kremlin-led efforts to interfere with U.S. elections By @holymolya Updated Jan. 12, 2017 4:23 p.m. ET 
MOSCOW—Russians named in an unverified dossier on President-elect Donald Trump reacted with incredulity to allegations they were tied to Kremlin-led efforts to interfere with the U.S. elections. 
The dossier contains claims that Russian officials have compromising evidence about Mr. Trump’s behavior that could be used to blackmail him, and that the Kremlin colluded with members of Mr. Trump’s team to help get him elected.
